*
 * generates code for model file
 * @public
 * @param {Object} inputSchema - schema of the type
 * @param {string} templatesDirectory - name of the templates directory
 * @param {string} User - name of the user model
 * @param {string} part - the template which should be returned
 * @return {string} model_code
 * @example
 *  repository = {
 *    "header": <template source> 
 *    "class": <template source>
 *    "methods": {
 *      "constructor": <template source>,
 *      "authRole": <template source>,
 *      "findOneById": <template source>,
 *      "find": <template source>,
 *      ... : ...
 *      "insert": <template source>,
 *      "updateById": <template source>,
 *      "removeById": <template source>,
 *    }
 *  }
